com.att.aro.model

Class AnalysisFilter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.att.aro.model.AnalysisFilter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class AnalysisFilter
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Represents a filter used for filtering information from a trace analysis based on a specified time range and set of ApplicationSelection objects.
    See Also:
